  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3204480/extras/4fa99c37df612fcb9c3865b78aa9ed03.avif?t=1750869101\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3204480/extras_big/4fa99c37df612fcb9c3865b78aa9ed03.avif?t=1750869101 width=800 height=151 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Inspired by arcade classics like Bubble Bobble and Snow Bros, Wispy Dreams delivers a modernized take on the beloved genre that fans have been waiting for. Bash enemies into each other with a variety of kicks, and watch your score soar as you chain them together.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3204480/extras/fa76c7c3e571a9530a548c67bc7db3dc.poster.avif?t=1750869101\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3204480/extras/fa76c7c3e571a9530a548c67bc7db3dc.webm?t=1750869101\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3204480/extras/fa76c7c3e571a9530a548c67bc7db3dc.mp4?t=1750869101\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3204480/extras/4c8dc74cbe9bb198457952cefbd4e682.avif?t=1750869101\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3204480/extras_big/4c8dc74cbe9bb198457952cefbd4e682.avif?t=1750869101 width=800 height=151 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The Wispy Isles are in danger! A mysterious force is taking over the minds and spirits of all the land's creatures. Those you call \"Guardians\" have been powerless to stop it. Looks like it's up to you to restore harmony to the Isles, and perhaps make some friends along the way!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3204480/extras/75e9bcdd0a80ddb4e3fbd4e5294fca80.avif?t=1750869101\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3204480/extras_big/75e9bcdd0a80ddb4e3fbd4e5294fca80.avif?t=1750869101 width=800 height=151 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The name of the game is to clear all the enemies on the screen to continue. But there's a twist - a magical key will appear and reawaken your foes. Bring it to the Gear Lock in time, or else you might get a visit from a not so friendly face. If you make it all the way to the world's boss, brace yourself for a tough fight. But wait, have you found all the secret items along the way?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3204480/extras/97e1067d42cb3a2b91f803cee30728cf.poster.avif?t=1750869101\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3204480/extras/97e1067d42cb3a2b91f803cee30728cf.webm?t=1750869101\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3204480/extras/97e1067d42cb3a2b91f803cee30728cf.mp4?t=1750869101\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3204480/extras/472f1155a30424fc2897ed788e8fc6bc.avif?t=1750869101\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3204480/extras_big/472f1155a30424fc2897ed788e8fc6bc.avif?t=1750869101 width=800 height=151 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 7 worlds to explore  </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 20 enemies to pummel  </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 9 bosses to fight  </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 3 endings to discover  </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Tons of powerups to collect   </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Loads of secrets to find   </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Alternate difficulties and game modes to unlock   </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Lovingly hand drawn artwork and animation   </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A beautiful and varied orchestral soundtrack</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3204480/extras/41526d0fc5c5ea5f137a654ed3d4ed16.avif?t=1750869101\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3204480/extras_big/41526d0fc5c5ea5f137a654ed3d4ed16.avif?t=1750869101 width=800 height=450 /></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3204480/extras/4fa99c37df612fcb9c3865b78aa9ed03.avif?t=1750869101\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3204480/extras_big/4fa99c37df612fcb9c3865b78aa9ed03.avif?t=1750869101 width=800 height=151 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Inspired by arcade classics like Bubble Bobble and Snow Bros, Wispy Dreams delivers a modernized take on the beloved genre that fans have been waiting for. Bash enemies into each other with a variety of kicks, and watch your score soar as you chain them together.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3204480/extras/fa76c7c3e571a9530a548c67bc7db3dc.poster.avif?t=1750869101\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3204480/extras/fa76c7c3e571a9530a548c67bc7db3dc.webm?t=1750869101\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3204480/extras/fa76c7c3e571a9530a548c67bc7db3dc.mp4?t=1750869101\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3204480/extras/4c8dc74cbe9bb198457952cefbd4e682.avif?t=1750869101\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3204480/extras_big/4c8dc74cbe9bb198457952cefbd4e682.avif?t=1750869101 width=800 height=151 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The Wispy Isles are in danger! A mysterious force is taking over the minds and spirits of all the land's creatures. Those you call \"Guardians\" have been powerless to stop it. Looks like it's up to you to restore harmony to the Isles, and perhaps make some friends along the way!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3204480/extras/75e9bcdd0a80ddb4e3fbd4e5294fca80.avif?t=1750869101\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3204480/extras_big/75e9bcdd0a80ddb4e3fbd4e5294fca80.avif?t=1750869101 width=800 height=151 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The name of the game is to clear all the enemies on the screen to continue. But there's a twist - a magical key will appear and reawaken your foes. Bring it to the Gear Lock in time, or else you might get a visit from a not so friendly face. If you make it all the way to the world's boss, brace yourself for a tough fight. But wait, have you found all the secret items along the way?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3204480/extras/97e1067d42cb3a2b91f803cee30728cf.poster.avif?t=1750869101\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3204480/extras/97e1067d42cb3a2b91f803cee30728cf.webm?t=1750869101\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3204480/extras/97e1067d42cb3a2b91f803cee30728cf.mp4?t=1750869101\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3204480/extras/472f1155a30424fc2897ed788e8fc6bc.avif?t=1750869101\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3204480/extras_big/472f1155a30424fc2897ed788e8fc6bc.avif?t=1750869101 width=800 height=151 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 7 worlds to explore  </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 20 enemies to pummel  </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 9 bosses to fight  </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 3 endings to discover  </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Tons of powerups to collect   </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Loads of secrets to find   </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Alternate difficulties and game modes to unlock   </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Lovingly hand drawn artwork and animation   </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A beautiful and varied orchestral soundtrack</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3204480/extras/41526d0fc5c5ea5f137a654ed3d4ed16.avif?t=1750869101\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3204480/extras_big/41526d0fc5c5ea5f137a654ed3d4ed16.avif?t=1750869101 width=800 height=450 /></span></p>",
